Lip Fullness: Medium to full. Your lips are well-defined and balanced.
Neck & Body
Neck Length: Average. It provides enough "clearance" for longer hair or high collars.
Neck Width: Average. It matches your facial proportions.
Shoulder Width: Average to Broad. You have a solid frame that supports volume on top of the head without looking top-heavy.
Overall Body Frame: Average.
Hair (Current)
Texture: Wavy/Curly. You have a lot of natural "S" patterns and volume.
Density: Thick. You have a significant amount of hair, which is great for building structure.
